NAME:	protocols-test-sh

DESCRIPTION:	This is the main script that submits all jobs to test stage-in and  stage-out with different protocols

INPUT: None

OUTPUT:		Job Tickets for all the jobs submitted

USAGE/EXAMPLE:		./protocols-test-sh
	
LIMITATIONS:	Should have properly set all the environment variables in inputfile.txt

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FOR ALL THE FOLLOWING JSDL FILES, CHANGE THE HOSTNAME, USERNAME, PASSWORD, TESTDIR accordingly if running seperately.
Note that the test scripts cat.sh and hostname.sh should be copied to the location X_TESTDIR (for scp, http, sftp etc); these files must be present to be staged in to the grid.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NAME:	cat-gffs.jsdl
	
DESCRIPTION:	Submits a single 'cat' job to specified BES, file staging uses ByteIO protocol

INPUT:	N/A

OUTPUT: Ticket Number for the job

USAGE/EXAMPLE: <GenesisII-Install-Dir>/grid run --jsdl=local:<local-path>/cat-gffs.jsdl  <BES-path> 

LIMITATIONS: None

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NAME: 	cat-scp.jsdl

DESCRIPTION:	Submits a single 'cat' job to specified BES, file staging uses  SCP protocol

INPUT: N/A

OUTPUT:	Ticket Number for the job

USAGE/EXAMPLE: <GenesisII-Install-Dir>/grid run --jsdl=local:<local-path>/cat-scp.jsdl  <BES-path> 

LIMITATIONS: None

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NAME:	cat-http.jsdl

DESCRIPTION:	Submits a single 'cat' job to specified BES, file staging uses HTTP protocol 

INPUT: 	N/A

OUTPUT: Ticket Number for the job

USAGE/EXAMPLE: <GenesisII-Install-Dir>/grid run --jsdl=local:<local-path>/cat-http.jsdl  <BES-path> 

LIMITATIONS: None

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NAME:  cat-ftp.jsdl

DESCRIPTION:	Submits a single 'cat' job to specified BES, file staging uses FTP protocol

INPUT: N/A

